      "description": "This car is in mint condition. The exterior is free of dents, scratches, and paint defects. The interior shows no signs of wear \u2014 upholstery, surfaces, and components are all in like-new condition. Mechanically, the vehicle is fully sound with no known issues. This is an exceptionally well-preserved example.",
