    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Ready for a new chapter \u2014 priced to move! This vehicle is in poor condition, and we're being completely upfront: it has visible wear, cosmetic issues, and mechanical needs that will require attention before it's road-ready. That said, the right buyer \u2014 a hands-on DIYer, a mechanic, or someone looking for a budget-friendly project \u2014 could find real value here. At this price point, you're getting an honest deal with room to make it your own!",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition \u2014 a used car that requires significant attention and is priced accordingly. The exterior shows substantial wear, including noticeable dents, scratches, and paint deterioration that go beyond typical cosmetic blemishes. The interior has seen heavy use, with worn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general fatigue throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will likely require repairs before it can be relied upon for regular daily driving. This listing is best suited for buyers who are mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or seeking parts \u2014 and who fully understand and accept the car's current state. There are no illusions here: this is a high-mileage, well-worn vehicle being sold as-is, and the price reflects exactly that.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 $7,500 - A budget-friendly opportunity for the right buyer! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has visible wear, some mechanical issues, and will need attention before it's running at its best. That said, it could be a solid project car or a parts vehicle for someone with the skills and vision to bring it back to life. Priced to reflect its current state, so what you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises here!",
      "price": 7500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Fixer-Upper with Potential! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has significant mechanical and/or cosmetic issues that will require attention, so it's best suited for a handy DIYer, a parts sourcer, or someone looking for a project car. It does have value for the right buyer who's willing to put in some work! Priced accordingly to reflect its current state \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we're being straight with you. If you've got the skills or the vision, this could be a rewarding find at a great entry price!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and it truly lives up to that description. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 the paint retains its deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, chips, or blemishes, and every panel aligns perfectly. The interior is equally impressive, showing no signs of wear: the upholstery is pristine, all surfaces are clean and unmarked, and every feature and control functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with all mechanical systems performing at their best. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and presents as close to new as a used car can get. A thorough pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged \u2014 we are confident this car will exceed your expectations.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a car in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but buyers should go in with clear expectations about its current state. The exterior shows visible wear consistent with its age and use: there are several scratches, some paint fading, and minor dents that have not been repaired. It's not a showroom car, but the body is structurally sound with no significant rust compromising the frame. Inside, the cabin reflects regular use \u2014 the upholstery has worn spots and some staining, and a few trim pieces show their age, though the dashboard and controls remain functional. Mechanically, the engine starts reliably and the car moves under its own power, but a pre-purchase inspection is strongly recommended, as there are likely maintenance items that will need attention in the near term. This is a practical option for a budget-conscious buyer who is comfortable with a project or a daily driver that isn't perfect.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    }
